data.description: Short sale. Subject to third party approval. Immaculate Home from top to bottom. Mr. and Mrs. Clean lived here. Hard wood floors in the dining room and living room. Fireplace in living room. New appliances in kitchen. Deck off of kitchen. Original wood work throughout the home. Three bedrooms with large closets on second floor. Deck off of hallway on second floor. Clean unfinished attic that can easily be converted to another bedroom if necessary. Basement is partially finished with a full bath with shower. New washer and dryer. Plenty of storage space. Garage is new and oversized. Back yard is fenced in and nicely landscaped. New front porch 2022. New furnace 2022. New air conditioning 2022. New roof 2022. Basement has glass blocked windows. Point of sale attached. Property is being sold as is. Buyer to assume POS.
